summary: This document includes a response cover sheet from the National Compliance Center to FBI Special Agent Gavin Gumbinner, along with a declaration of authenticity of AT&T records by Kristin Chandler. It contains subscriber information and call details for various accounts, as well as a subpoena for testimony before a grand jury.
